name: Childhood Dreams
description:
Time: 11:44pm
*The portal will open in 3…2…1…* 

Oh! Welcome to my local Taguara back in Maturín, Venezuela.
It has been 15 years since I last went.

 Mmmm… I guess some faces are blurry but I feel the same, the same spark, the same childhood magic listening to my abuelos playing domino while Simón Díaz plays in the background. Oh how I miss those times …

I wish I was big enough to buy a Chigüi Beer! Oh.. wait… it’s my dream so I guess I can! 

SALUD! 

-

o｡.♡ FROM THE COLLECTION DREAMS & PORTALS ♡.｡o

Close your eyes and relax ˘◡˘
Welcome to your subconscious mind, where you can go deep into childhood memories, constant internal battles and how to use this amazing portal to heal and discover new aspects within you.
